(When are we going to get Terrorsaur on-line?)



Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw stood up straight and put her hands on her hips. "You refer me to 
Dinobot again, and I will seriously rearrange your spark plugs!" She 
frowned. "Before I go after Megatron, I want repairs. Your little minons 
damaged me. A damage bot cannot do much against someone like Megatron. I've 
learned that."
